<title>USA: Network Long Distance names Crawford chmn.</title>
<headline>Network Long Distance names Crawford chmn.</headline>
<dateline>BATON ROUGE, La. 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Network Long Distance Inc said Thursday that it has named John Crawford chairman of the board and chief executive officer, and that Thomas Keefe has been named chief financial officer.</p>
<p>Crawford replaces Michael Ross, who will remain a member of the board of directors.</p>
<p>Crawford previously served as chairman and CEO of Eastern Telecom International Corp, which merged with Netowrk Long Distance this year.</p>
<p>Keefe most recently served as chief financial officer of Eastern.</p>
